{"tid":444982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"決意離開連登 這是我在這裡出的最後一個post","createTime":"2017-10-23T03:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T06:18:20.000Z","uid":31314,"like":14,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"80bddad645c0fa610f8602b267ae0b619ec8b800","tid":444982,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"這裏的人學識都很高 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從這裏的人的留言中學會了很多知識 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n溝女, 地理, 9up, 歷史, 政治 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是我一上網就立刻到波台的原因 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正正是因為我自己都是一個愛好知識的人 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上這裏的人都多廿靚歲的, 同我相若, 岩傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我在這裡出了很多很多post, 但99%都是所謂的 &quot;假膠post&quot;, 即是完完全全亂up老作搏大家一笑, <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帖內的內容和自己的事完全沒關, 無論出post同reply都係, 甚至好多時同真實既自己係相反 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明是曼聯球迷, 卻經常出post揶揄死獌狗 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明自己都係廢柴, 卻經常出post話其他人係垃圾 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明自己覺得麻友唔差, 就出post話佢係G <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歸根究抵都係純粹因為工作時無聊, 所以無無聊聊地出個post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講無聊野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後一邊工作, 一邊睇回覆, 自娛一下 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這件事對不喜歡現在的工作的我十分重要 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時, 我故意講相反野, 因為驚俾人知我既真正身份 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個知...就會話俾另一個知, 然後一傳十, 十傳百, 就不好了, 我完全唔想俾人知我o係網上既身份, 講過 d 乜 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾人知道, 我o係呢度暢所欲言, 說傻話, 減減壓的空間就完全被破壞了... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(雖然我出既post都同自己做過既野無關) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過, 有一日我忽然發現自己沉迷了這裡....荒廢正業 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離開, 因為不想再在這裏浪費時間了, 往後我還有很多計劃, 操番好體能, 籌備上富士山, 練番水, 練好 d 足球, 考A0, , 重投放下了一年多的義工活動, 抽多 d 時間搵女朋友, 考番Master ..etc etc <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再見了, 波台各位高學識既人.多謝各位陪左我咁多個晚上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://25.media.tumblr.com/92ba88e4600749872175ce8a2f9ce725/tumblr_mj1y1mCDAU1qaorn7o4_r1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F25.media.tumblr.com%2F92ba88e4600749872175ce8a2f9ce725%2Ftumblr_mj1y1mCDAU1qaorn7o4_r1_400.gif&h=40c8a292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/VelWewgR6CpNK/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FVelWewgR6CpNK%2Fgiphy.gif&h=90e26383&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bb500a21d8780b4e49946b616274545d7610557","tid":444982,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:14:49.000Z","msg":"挽留. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190f6dae24c15125744d6006dd7ef4f4b2043b64","tid":444982,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:15:03.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"190198b4add1b8bef9a71a731d9b2cc6d2eebb87","tid":444982,"uid":4349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"你女朋友帽左你喎<br />\n仲一齊好咩"},{"pid":"2c286643fb1f9f33202dbc971766936b277e470a","tid":444982,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:17:54.000Z","msg":"快D走啦"},{"pid":"b98c0e38784034c2bd19e7013d5876f5442083db","tid":444982,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"返去搵肥媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a72dea581570cca3b4c7efb58a04815c451e34e","tid":444982,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返去搵肥媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都走囉<br />\n洗唔洗貢串牙奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1cb38622924f66eabcf663457e8e9229852412","tid":444982,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快D走啦</blockquote><br />\n再見豬蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9205d945043593d6a36091044e99946920a0ce","tid":444982,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockqu